This paper deals with the problem of generating pairwise comparison labels for machine learning tasks, which is a common problem in the field of machine learning. The paper proposes an algorithmic approach to accelerate the process of generating pairwise comparison labels. This problem is closely related to the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures (cs.DS), computer vision (cs.CV), and statistics (cs.ST). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
